organic.title: St. Vincent de Paul Juneau – Serving Juneau since 1984
organic.snippet: Stop by 8617 Teal Street and fill out a housing application. You may contact our housing assistant. St. Vincent's also has a navigator on site from 9am to 1pm ...

organic.title: Administrative Offices - St. Vincent de Paul Juneau
organic.snippet: Located in the first floor of Smith Hall at 8617 Teal Street in the Valley behind the Nugget Mall. Office Hours: Monday – Friday, 9 am to 4 pm.

organic.title: St. Vincent de Paul - Juneau, AK
organic.snippet: St. Vincent de Paul's Society mission is to provide material and spiritual charity, and work for social justice, for all people. Visit Our Website
